<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MITH Sports AI — Player Intelligence Platform</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background: #0a0e1a;
    color: white;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Background subtle grid */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    padding: 28px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.2);
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: white;
  }

  .logo span {
    color: #2E75B6;
  }

  .logo-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #2E75B6;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .nav-badge {
    background: rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.4);
    color: #2E75B6;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    padding: 100px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #2E75B6;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero h1 .highlight {
    color: #2E75B6;
  }

  .hero p {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #2E75B6;
    color: white;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover { background: #1F5A9E; }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(46,117,182,0.4), transparent);
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  /* STATS BAR */
  .stats-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 60px 0;
  }

  .stat {
    background: #0a0e1a;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #2E75B6;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* FEATURES */
  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #2E75B6;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-heading {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.5);
    background: rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.05);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: white;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* THE DIFFERENCE */
  .difference {
    background: rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .difference blockquote {
    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .difference blockquote span {
    color: #2E75B6;
  }

  .difference cite {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.15);
    border: 2px solid #2E75B6;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #2E75B6;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: white;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ORIGIN */
  .origin {
    border-left: 3px solid #2E75B6;
    padding: 32px 40px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    background: rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .origin h3 {
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #2E75B6;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .origin p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .origin p strong {
    color: white;
  }

  /* COMING SOON */
  .coming-soon {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.2);
  }

  .coming-soon h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .coming-soon p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .email-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    max-width: 440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .email-form input {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 240px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46, 117, 182, 0.4);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    outline: none;
  }

  .email-form input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
  .email-form input:focus { border-color: #2E75B6; }

  .email-form button {
    background: #2E75B6;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .email-form button:hover { background: #1F5A9E; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    padding: 32px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  footer .logo { font-size: 18px; }

  footer p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero { padding: 60px 0 48px; }
    .stats-bar { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .difference { padding: 32px 24px; }
    .origin { padding: 24px; }
    footer { justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div>
      <div class="logo">MITH<span>.</span></div>
      <div class="logo-sub">Sports AI</div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-badge">Coming Soon</div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">AI-Powered Player Intelligence</div>
    <h1>
      Find the players<br>
      <span class="highlight">nobody else can see.</span>
    </h1>
    <p>
      MITH Sports AI analyzes game film to surface player impact that never appears in a box score. Built for college basketball programs navigating the transfer portal.
    </p>
    <a href="#notify" class="hero-cta">Get Early Access</a>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">15</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Day Portal Window</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">1,500+</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Portal Players Annually</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number">0</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Tools That Watch Film</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <div class="section-title">What MITH Does</div>
  <div class="section-heading">Intelligence that lives<br>in the film.</div>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
      <h3>True Impact Score</h3>
      <p>A proprietary player valuation model that measures total impact on winning — including and especially the contributions that never appear in a box score.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
      <h3>AI Film Analysis</h3>
      <p>Upload the film you already have. MITH's AI watches every possession and extracts behavioral data — off-ball movement, defensive positioning, screen intelligence, effort — automatically.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Role Gap Detection</h3>
      <p>Identifies players being used in the wrong role whose true value is hidden from every traditional scouting tool. The diamond-in-the-rough signal, surfaced systematically.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
      <h3>NIL Valuation Layer</h3>
      <p>The Impact-to-Cost Ratio connects True Impact Score to NIL market data — so programs know whether a player's ask is justified before the negotiation begins.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🏀</div>
      <h3>Scheme Fit Intelligence</h3>
      <p>Every program runs a different system. MITH maps players to your specific scheme — not a generic standard — surfacing fits that conventional recruiting never finds.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
      <h3>Confidence Indicator</h3>
      <p>Every score carries a reliability rating based on possession volume and film data. You always know exactly how much to trust the number you are looking at.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- THE DIFFERENCE -->
  <div class="difference">
    <blockquote>
      "Every other tool tells coaches<br>
      what a player <span>scored.</span><br>
      We tell them what a player <span>is worth.</span>"
    </blockquote>
    <cite>— The MITH Difference</cite>
  </div>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <div class="section-title">How It Works</div>
  <div class="section-heading">Three steps.<br>One unfair advantage.</div>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <h3>Upload Film</h3>
      <p>Connect your existing film library or upload directly. Works with Hudl and major platforms. No new hardware required.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <h3>AI Analyzes</h3>
      <p>MITH watches every possession. Tracks 25 behavioral variables across all three buckets — on-ball, off-ball, and team impact.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <h3>Find Your Players</h3>
      <p>Ranked player cards. True Impact Scores. Role Gap alerts. NIL valuations. Everything your staff needs in a 15-day window.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ORIGIN STORY -->
  <div class="origin">
    <h3>The Name</h3>
    <p>
      In basketball, <strong>Mouse in the House</strong> describes the overlooked player who wins the matchup anyway — not through size or reputation, but through intelligence, positioning, and qualities nobody was measuring. <strong>MITH finds that player.</strong> Systematically. At scale. Before anyone else does.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- COMING SOON / EMAIL CAPTURE -->
  <div class="coming-soon" id="notify">
    <h2>Built for the 2027<br>portal window.</h2>
    <p>
      MITH is currently in development. Join the waitlist for early access and be the first program to find what everyone else is missing.
    </p>
    <div class="email-form">
      <input type="email" placeholder="your@program.edu" />
      <button type="button">Join Waitlist</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <div>
      <div class="logo">MITH<span style="color:#2E75B6;">.</span></div>
      <div class="logo-sub">Sports AI</div>
    </div>
    <p>© 2026 MITH Sports AI &nbsp;·&nbsp; MITHsports.ai &nbsp;·&nbsp; Confidential</p>
  </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
